Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.03,0:00:04.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens, I'm still your partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.98,0:00:06.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With a chilling event coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.64,0:00:09.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the Detective Boys build a snowman,\Nforging the tracks of the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:10.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Recognizing that single truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.92,0:00:12.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A child with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.44,0:00:14.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.29,0:02:15.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nicely done, Shinichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.79,0:02:20.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah... So great, so great.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.67,0:02:26.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Unsmashable Snowman, Part One!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.72,0:02:32.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where is everybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.35,0:02:35.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, they're over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.48,0:02:45.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, they said they'd let me teach them to snowboard earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.98,0:02:47.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now all they wanna do is build a snowman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.49,0:02:50.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, regardless, is everything alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.66,0:02:54.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With that boy who saw Mizunashi Rena's motorcycle accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.54,0:02:59.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was thinking that the foreign woman helmet may have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.04,0:03:04.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that woman from the Black Organization...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.30,0:03:06.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vermouth, I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:08.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What'd you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.51,0:03:09.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.72,0:03:11.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you get it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.72,0:03:17.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means they already know about her accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.18,0:03:20.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they almost definitely know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.44,0:03:25.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About Mizunashi Rena's injuries and hospitalization.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.52,0:03:27.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shinichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.82,0:03:29.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's all they know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.32,0:03:32.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They definitely don't know where.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.11,0:03:37.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, I already told Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}\Nfrom the FBI about that case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.37,0:03:42.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The FBI won't let her be found easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.67,0:03:45.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, is the boy alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.46,0:03:50.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The FBI is protecting and watching over him as of now,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.09,0:03:53.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I don't believe the organization's interested in him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.22,0:03:57.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they wanted to kill him, they would've done it earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.01,0:03:59.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But isn't it strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.10,0:04:04.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That the house where a murder occurred...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.15,0:04:08.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is also Where the boy who met that woman lived?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.03,0:04:10.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.36,0:04:12.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was concerned as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.20,0:04:17.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I looked Mizunashi Rena up on the\Nnet and found something interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.83,0:04:21.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A big fan's homepage dedicated to\Nthe announcer Mizunashi Rena.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.21,0:04:23.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then it hit me:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.92,0:04:29.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was the guy who was hired for that strange\Njob and was an indirect cause of that case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.96,0:04:34.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One day, he was wearing his custom\Njacket with her picture on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.30,0:04:37.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When something strange happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.47,0:04:40.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"When I finished the job and was on my way home,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.22,0:04:44.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,some kid pointed at my jacket saying,\N'I saw her fly off her motorcycle!'
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.27,0:04:47.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His said his name was Touji."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.56,0:04:51.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that means that guy read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.98,0:04:52.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.03,0:04:53.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.28,0:04:59.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The guy who connected that murder\Ncase, the boy, and the strange job...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.54,0:05:05.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The guy who lead Uncle Kogoro and myself\Nto a case which took us to the boy's house...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.29,0:05:09.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The guy who had me meet that boy again...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:11.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hondou Eisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.96,0:05:14.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hondou Eisuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.67,0:05:17.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a transfer student at Ran's school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.14,0:05:21.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His eyes are identical to Mizunashi Rena's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.39,0:05:26.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey, don't tell me that transfer student...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.19,0:05:33.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They could have sent him to locate Mizunashi Rena.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.07,0:05:37.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's just one possibility, but, that guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.74,0:05:38.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.91,0:05:43.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't really describe it, he just doesn't seem evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.54,0:05:48.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiot! What if that's their plan,\Nto make you lower your guard!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.00,0:05:50.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.63,0:05:51.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:05:58.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't I mention it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.51,0:06:00.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The saw, nails, and hammer case?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.35,0:06:03.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He cried at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.64,0:06:10.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It may have been that he was angry he couldn't solve the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.81,0:06:13.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or maybe it was because he knew the answer,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:19.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but couldn't think of a way to show it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.57,0:06:21.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then, he did cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:24.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It just looks like its crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.50,0:06:28.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.54,0:06:32.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks more like an alien, doesn't it, Mitsuhiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.09,0:06:33.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.96,0:06:36.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a great idea to buy fruit on the way here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.09,0:06:37.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.80,0:06:42.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you kids! Don't touch that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.53,0:06:45.95,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kokura Sakuko (22)\NUniversity Student
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.11,0:06:46.22,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,That's our graduation project.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.97,0:06:49.11,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,That's only the outline, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.04,0:06:49.00,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kiyama Tanji (22)\NUniversity Student
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.23,0:06:51.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a graduation project?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.44,0:06:53.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this a snow model?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.90,0:06:54.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.32,0:06:57.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We re students at a sculpturing art college.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.42,0:07:03.97,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Onoue Asaka (22)\NUniversity Student
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.51,0:07:00.62,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,We four love snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:03.98,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,So much what we begged our professor to let us do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.33,0:07:07.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it looks like this guy's the only one working on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.80,0:07:11.79,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Well, it isn't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.14,0:07:13.27,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Itabashi Kazuya (22)\N{\fs16} University Student
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:14.99,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I make the starting form before we discuss the figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:17.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we're done, we take a picture with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.17,0:07:20.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and call it our final snow sculpture.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.01,0:07:24.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At first, everyone does their own part,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.89,0:07:27.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,which helps me do the frame.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.27,0:07:30.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We named it "The Grieving Snowman. "
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:35.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The head's basically finished,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:36.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but the body isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.23,0:07:39.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.03,0:07:41.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.36,0:07:43.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're leaving the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.24,0:07:45.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't hurry and finish the frame...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.70,0:07:48.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't say that, Sakuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.79,0:07:51.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Itabashi stayed just for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.87,0:07:56.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can put it that way, but doing a four\Nperson project was you three's idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.25,0:07:58.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never agreed to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.38,0:08:02.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now, this is our last winter vacation as university students.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.59,0:08:05.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right, this may be our last time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.89,0:08:09.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We four may never be together again after graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.97,0:08:10.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Asaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.10,0:08:11.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.39,0:08:14.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:18.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't the four of us go night-skiing to celebrate?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.03,0:08:24.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right, not all of us can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.45,0:08:27.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sakuko! Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.24,0:08:31.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Asaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.33,0:08:34.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.58,0:08:36.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's already decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.33,0:08:40.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, bye for now, we'll be inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.80,0:08:42.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let us know then you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.59,0:08:43.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.39,0:08:48.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That brunette's foot...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.60,0:08:49.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's dragging it on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.35,0:08:53.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really don't like that woman with the almond-shaped eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:57.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's surprise them with our snowman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.15,0:08:59.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.57,0:09:00.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First of all...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.35,0:09:31.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakuko here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.14,0:09:33.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Talk with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.64,0:09:35.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:41.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew we'd get curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.57,0:09:43.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Especially after all the work we did on the snowman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.57,0:09:44.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:47.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All you guys did was make a snowman...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.66,0:09:48.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.91,0:09:49.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.41,0:09:55.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe she went skiing by herself and can't\Nfind her way back due to the snow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.25,0:09:57.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, Asaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.21,0:10:01.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.09,0:10:04.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the old man who was with those kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.42,0:10:08.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakuko, the one who was with us earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.72,0:10:10.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,wasn't in her room when we went to get her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.35,0:10:13.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've already checked the shops.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.22,0:10:15.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe she really is out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.35,0:10:18.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's split up and look anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.31,0:10:23.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll search around the lodge, you guys look in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.11,0:10:26.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sakuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.65,0:10:28.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.40,0:10:30.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you, woman with the almond-shaped eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.99,0:10:36.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.46,0:10:43.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guys... Where are you all?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.04,0:10:46.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.18,0:10:53.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stupid, stop crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.05,0:10:56.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold onto my jacket and don't let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.64,0:11:00.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys staying together?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.35,0:11:04.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is holding onto my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.07,0:11:06.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the---!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.32,0:11:07.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's my hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.74,0:11:10.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, you sure it's my hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.07,0:11:15.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, isn't searching during a whiteout like this useless?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.33,0:11:19.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we should continue after the storm settles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.88,0:11:28.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our snowman's head fell off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.46,0:11:29.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.80,0:11:33.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The wind must have blown it off...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.80,0:11:35.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The glove!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.89,0:11:37.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:38.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Genta!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.39,0:11:39.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That glove!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.27,0:11:40.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a cliff there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.56,0:11:44.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.94,0:11:46.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.07,0:11:49.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, at least the storm has let up, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:50.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.11,0:11:55.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.37,0:11:57.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the lake down there...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.99,0:11:58.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that floating?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.00,0:12:02.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.21,0:12:04.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Use the magnifying function of your glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:05.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:10.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can see someone down there...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.67,0:12:12.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.26,0:12:19.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.00,0:12:29.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The deceased is Kokura Sakuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, 22 years old,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:31.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a fourth year art student.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.89,0:12:35.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cause of death looks like drowning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.97,0:12:39.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should I schedule an autopsy regardless, Yamamura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.89,0:12:42.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but also...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.44,0:12:47.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, was she traveling alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.32,0:12:53.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, she came with her three classmates from their art school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.99,0:12:55.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the right: Kiyama Tanji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.37,0:12:57.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Onoue Asaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.12,0:12:59.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and Itabashi Kazuya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.33,0:13:03.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, those three found the body?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.17,0:13:05.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it was found by...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.21,0:13:07.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Us, the Detective Boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.21,0:13:11.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were going through the snowstorm to find her...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:13.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And spotted her body from up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:18.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was floating in the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.93,0:13:20.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're that boy that's always with Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.10,0:13:23.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, of course, Detective Mouri is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.06,0:13:25.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.44,0:13:27.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, it's just us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.69,0:13:29.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh... Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:36.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means we won't be able to see\NSleeping Kogorou solve this cursed case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.66,0:13:38.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cursed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.62,0:13:39.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.33,0:13:45.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On her feet: snowboarding boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:48.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the lake: a snowboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.88,0:13:59.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see, to get to the lake below the cliff, you\Nhave to get across the bridge by car, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:02.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bridge was blocked until we got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.02,0:14:05.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then she fell while riding her snowboard?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.31,0:14:09.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, it's natural to assume she rode off accidentally...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.82,0:14:16.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then fell into the lake and drowned.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:18.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.74,0:14:21.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This lake, I mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.58,0:14:23.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The lake?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:28.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You haven't noticed? There's so much\Nsnow, but the lake hasn't frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.92,0:14:32.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There must be a creature lurking under the surface doing this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.92,0:14:35.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which is what sucked Sakuko san into the lake!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:37.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the hot springs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.26,0:14:43.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The water from the hot springs flows\Ninto this lake, keeping it warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.68,0:14:47.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though, it isn't a safe temperature for people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.98,0:14:50.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've heard it never freezes over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.44,0:14:52.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.15,0:14:56.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's stated in the guidebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:14:59.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't a local police officer know this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.95,0:15:03.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, I guess it was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:07.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But still, I wonder if she was really snowboarding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.04,0:15:12.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because this woman isn't wearing a hat or goggles.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.55,0:15:18.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true, I don't think anyone would go snowboarding\Nduring a snowstorm without something on their head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.76,0:15:22.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It probably came off when she fell in the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.51,0:15:24.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That could be for the hat or the goggles...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.35,0:15:27.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But gloves wouldn't come off, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.73,0:15:28.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.60,0:15:31.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, that means Kokura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.40,0:15:36.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Must sweat a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:37.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.61,0:15:40.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.07,0:15:43.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some people don't wear gloves because their hands get sweaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.41,0:15:47.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But still, you need gloves for snow boarding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.87,0:15:53.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe someone put boots on her because she\Nwasn't originally dressed for snowboarding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.67,0:15:58.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone may have murdered Sakuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and made it look like...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:15:59.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A snowboarding accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.22,0:16:01.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.85,0:16:05.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, it's one of those three?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.68,0:16:08.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe it's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.02,0:16:18.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, can you tell me about Sakuko san's\Nday up until her body was found?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.53,0:16:19.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:23.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We last saw her just before noon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.45,0:16:27.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Sakuko went to her room immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.87,0:16:35.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The four of us were going to meet at\N1:00 for lunch, but she didn't show.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.17,0:16:39.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We went to her room and knocked, but she didn't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.09,0:16:43.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, we asked the lodge staff to unlock the door,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.18,0:16:44.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and discovered she was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:49.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We three split up to look for her inside the lodge...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:51.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But found nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.73,0:16:53.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's when we came along.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.44,0:16:59.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe she went skiing by herself and can't\Nfind her way back due to the snow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.20,0:17:01.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, Asaka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:05.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.12,0:17:08.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the old man who was with those kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.41,0:17:12.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakuko, the one who was with us earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:14.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,wasn't in her room when we went to get her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.29,0:17:17.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've already checked the shops.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.17,0:17:19.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe she really is out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.34,0:17:22.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's split up and look anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:27.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll search around the lodge, you guys look in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:31.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then we split into two search groups,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.27,0:17:36.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,which is when Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} spotted her body from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:44.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you guys, where were you all from when you\Nleft her until you realized she was missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:47.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was in my room at the lodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.33,0:17:49.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was in my room as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.62,0:17:53.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was making a snowman behind the lodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:54.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A snowman?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.50,0:17:56.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.63,0:17:59.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a working version for our graduation project.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.09,0:18:04.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like Sakuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} rented a snowboard and boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.09,0:18:06.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you all as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.72,0:18:08.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I rented one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.35,0:18:12.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I rented a pair of skiis, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.56,0:18:13.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:15.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} hasn't skiied in awhile...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.23,0:18:20.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ever since I injured my leg last year and couldn't ski anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.78,0:18:26.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, you could still push someone over without skiing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.57,0:18:34.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, any of you three could have called her\Nto the top after you all split up earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.83,0:18:42.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arid pushed her right into the lake, making it look like she fell in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.01,0:18:46.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.68,0:18:50.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd make sense if she rode off on a speeding snowboard...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.64,0:18:56.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if she were just pushed off, she would\Nhave landed right about there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.48,0:18:59.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, it's still about five meters to the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.48,0:19:03.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, so it's impossible for her to have just been pushed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:06.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if you ski with her on your back...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.91,0:19:12.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think that's possible, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.29,0:19:19.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During a snowstorm, it'd be pretty difficult\Nto get back up there so quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.33,0:19:22.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even with a rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:29.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you still suspect me, you can go check\Nmy skiis and ski boots in lodge locker.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.01,0:19:31.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They would be wet if I used them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.22,0:19:34.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You three are using the same locker?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.85,0:19:35.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.68,0:19:42.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, the one who took her boots and snowboard\Ncould have been any one of you three, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.86,0:19:44.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what're you getting at?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.03,0:19:53.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, if you tied her to the snowboard\Nand pushed her over the cliff...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.79,0:19:58.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She would hit the lake, making a big splash!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:01.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling okay, Officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.83,0:20:03.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The slope is too bumpy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.96,0:20:08.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would flip over if you tried that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.09,0:20:12.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what about our snowboarder, Itabashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.76,0:20:15.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could angle it easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.60,0:20:19.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, where's the rope used to tie her to the board?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:21.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.36,0:20:24.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if it did make it there,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.94,0:20:28.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,wouldn't the body still be tied to the board?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.40,0:20:31.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And besides, she may not have her gloves on because...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.95,0:20:38.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She may have been trying to use her cell phone to call us for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.79,0:20:43.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why would she take off both gloves to use the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.29,0:20:46.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it was a text message.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.88,0:20:49.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She used both hands to do text messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.05,0:20:51.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A text message?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.51,0:20:52.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.30,0:21:01.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She always used to text people before calling them to\Nmake sure they could talk, saying, "Is now alright?"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.64,0:21:06.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While she was text messaging, the wind\Nprobably blew the gloves away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:13.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She may have been chasing them...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.25,0:21:23.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And accidentally fell off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.38,0:21:26.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was the snowstorm really that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.63,0:21:28.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it definitely was!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.71,0:21:32.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was so bad that all you could see was white!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.51,0:21:39.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guys... Where are you all?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.77,0:21:41.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess this was an accident after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.18,0:21:42.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.44,0:21:46.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you please stop accusing us now, Officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.23,0:21:51.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, anyway, let's head up there where she probably fell from.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.78,0:21:54.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We may find some traces of the accident there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.91,0:21:57.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Accident"? It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.16,0:22:01.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone about to meet their friends for lunch in an hour...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.66,0:22:04.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't drag a snowboard out in a snowstorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.25,0:22:10.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If this is a murder, the criminal is likely among those three.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.42,0:22:12.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's left...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.13,0:22:16.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is how they got Sakuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} from the lodge...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.02,0:22:22.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All the way down here...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.64,0:22:25.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To throw her in the lake.
